Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.51,0:02:05.52,Titles,,90,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Nearby War
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.25,0:02:21.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,…and that concludes the patrol flight schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.88,0:02:26.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.47,0:02:28.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Did they have permission to take off?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.56,0:02:34.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,We’re going to keep flying?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.16,0:02:36.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Weren’t you the one who said that if we didn’t fly a Simoun together,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.40,0:02:38.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,we wouldn’t know whether we were compatible or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.73,0:02:40.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is plenty!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.35,0:02:42.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,You’re amazing, Aaeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.90,0:02:44.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,So can’t we—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:46.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,We haven’t done a Ri Maajon yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.45,0:02:47.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let’s do the Stingray Ri Maajon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.21,0:02:58.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Way to go, Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:06.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morinas!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.97,0:03:09.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don’t get it! It’s too confusing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:18.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morinas, concentrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.58,0:03:19.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:21.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:13.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,I thought I ordered Chor Tempest to stand down until the rest of the new recruits arrive, Sibylla Aaeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.04,0:04:17.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,If we don’t practice while we can, we won’t be ready for the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.58,0:04:18.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then we’ll really be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:23.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then use a Simile—and get permission first!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.13,0:04:27.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru! Morinas!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.68,0:04:35.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why were you offering prayers without permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.55,0:04:37.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,That was no prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.22,0:04:38.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,We were training for battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.56,0:04:43.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why are you yelling at us, Paraietta?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.87,0:04:46.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,You’re not Chor Tempest’s regina.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.82,0:04:52.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Our choir’s regina, Neviril, is not feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:54.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Until she recovers, I am acting in her stead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:55.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.87,0:05:02.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do Paraietta and the Sibylla Aurea have {\i1}that{\i0} kind of special relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.35,0:05:22.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru! You forgot something!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.36,0:05:31.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,A kiss of gratitude, to thank Tempus Spatium after a Simoun flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.07,0:05:33.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don’t care about stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:36.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,You don’t like doing it with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.58,0:05:44.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wapourif… I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.14,0:05:46.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,I hope they don’t get mad at you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:50.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,When a sibylla tells us to let her fly, letting her fly is part of our job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.64,0:05:57.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Awfully cold, isn’t she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.35,0:06:00.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,She’s just a kid. You don’t have to tease her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.10,0:06:01.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Tease her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.35,0:06:02.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.23,0:06:06.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,But you know…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.02,0:06:09.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Flying with her was {\i1}sooo{\i0} wonderful…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:18.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.41,0:06:22.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,That was great, Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:26.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Which Ri Maajon were you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:29.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru, please don’t do things like that any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:31.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:34.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is everyone really okay with the way things are right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.34,0:06:39.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,When is Chor Tempest going to rejoin the other choirs on the shift rotation?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.18,0:06:42.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,If things don’t change…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:46.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,If they don’t, we’ll just go back to being regular Simoun sibyllae,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:50.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,offering prayers and waiting for our turn to visit the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.98,0:06:53.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,When my day comes, I’m going to choose to become a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.44,0:06:55.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can’t wait! Can you, Nee-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.20,0:07:00.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m also planning to become a man, Alti.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.45,0:07:04.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that how you all feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.37,0:07:08.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,That it’s okay if you never go into battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.34,0:07:16.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Looks like Chor Rubor has returned safely again…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.77,0:07:29.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,You were trying to do the Stingray Ri Maajon, weren’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.77,0:07:31.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Spoken like a true prodigy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.63,0:07:35.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,You couldn’t even pull off a simple thing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.36,0:07:39.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is this really Chor Tempest?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.70,0:07:46.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you like the rest of them, Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.41,0:07:50.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,D’you think it’s fine if you never go to battle or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.17,0:07:54.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,There isn’t a person alive who likes war, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.06,0:08:02.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru, we only want to perform our duties as priestesses in service to Tempus Spatium.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.11,0:08:05.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then get out here and perform them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.68,0:08:07.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’ll tell you this, Aaeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.97,0:08:11.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,You and I will never be a pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.16,0:08:27.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m Vyura, from Chor Rubor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.49,0:08:29.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,They said I’m to room with you starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.71,0:08:31.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:34.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m Aaeru, from Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.42,0:08:36.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,You’re s’posed to be an auriga, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.96,0:08:38.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Same as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.13,0:08:40.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,You know, for the longest time, Neviril has been—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.72,0:08:43.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Look, since Chor Tempest has been off duty,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.76,0:08:46.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,our choir has been split into two shifts,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:48.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,and we’ve been flying patrols around the clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.77,0:08:52.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,We’re in no position to slack off and play around like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.48,0:08:53.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just let me sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:09.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,I could show you the kind of flying that would satisfy even you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:10.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Maybe you could.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:11.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,C’mon, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.10,0:09:29.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,If we go now, then everyone should be in the cafeteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:30.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.48,0:09:32.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.56,0:09:34.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,If it’s dinner you’re worried about, I brought plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:36.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s not the problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:39.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:44.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Here, this is your share.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:45.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,And one more thing…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:49.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let’s go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.87,0:10:02.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Which Ri Maajon shall we start with?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.63,0:10:04.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Which ones do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.49,0:10:06.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don’t know…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.26,0:10:08.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,There’s got to be something, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.43,0:10:11.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Silver Ri Maajon, I guess…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:15.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that’s a good one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:19.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,But since we’re going to all this trouble anyway, let’s go find the enemy before we do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.09,0:10:22.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,You’re planning to get into a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:29.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,If we do, they can’t keep our choir off duty forever, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.04,0:10:31.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:33.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:47.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Isn’t that…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:49.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:55.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s a Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:11:01.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,The ones on patrol right now are the reservists from Chor Caput, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:02.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,What would they be doing down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.90,0:11:05.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,They might have been attacked by the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.35,0:11:07.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then they’ll have information about the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:10.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let’s make sure that the area is secure first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:15.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,There’s only one of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.46,0:11:17.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Fortune is smiling on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:19.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,This will be my final—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.48,0:11:42.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was Aaeru after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:44.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,And this time she took Limone with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:46.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.15,0:11:47.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,But she’s my pair…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:50.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,I got dumped, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.93,0:11:53.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s not really about being dumped…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.29,0:11:56.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Flying without permission again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:58.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Must be nice to be in a choir with so much free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:12:01.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest is going to get dissolved for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.00,0:12:02.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Looks like we’re going to get busier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:04.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Shouldn’t we report this to the dux?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.88,0:12:07.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,If we don’t bring them back, we’ll all be held responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:10.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why don’t we just leave them be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.39,0:12:14.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,If they want to fly, then let them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.14,0:12:18.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,They’re sure to be back by morning, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.52,0:12:21.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0} can’t go anywhere at the moment regardless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.48,0:12:26.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just what kind of priestess is this Aaeru, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.95,0:12:34.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,All I’m sure of is that she has a good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:35.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,A good reason for being here, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.56,0:12:57.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,A fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:01.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:03.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.21,0:13:05.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,You bastard…!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:16.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s right, we’re Simoun sibyllae.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:31.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,The pollution is eating into our bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.34,0:13:34.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,We need new technologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:38.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,The secret of the Simoun, kept hidden by the Theocracy…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.14,0:13:40.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,If we can obtain that…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.14,0:13:43.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,…we can say goodbye to this technology that poisons our skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.54,0:14:02.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’ve done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.96,0:14:05.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’ve captured a Simoun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:07.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m not just going to retire from the military…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:11.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Glory to the Archipelago!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:20.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m telling you, it won’t work!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.43,0:14:26.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,You Islanders don’t have the divine protection of Tempus Spatium!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:30.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,The only ones who can pilot a Simoun are priestesses who haven’t gone to the Spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.61,0:14:35.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those like us, who haven’t chosen whether to be male or female!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:24.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru, what are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.50,0:15:27.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Take back our Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.65,0:15:29.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Keep your voice down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.66,0:15:32.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s not like he can understand us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:34.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Archipelago wants our Simoun,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.34,0:15:38.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,because a Simoun is the only machine that can move through the sky with complete freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.22,0:15:40.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,But we’re not going to let them have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.10,0:15:41.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.22,0:15:47.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,My friends have all gone to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.35,0:15:49.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m the only one from my village who hasn’t gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.73,0:15:53.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why don’t you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:55.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because I don’t know what to choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.36,0:15:59.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do I want to become a man, or stay a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.73,0:16:03.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you can’t decide, Onashia can decide for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.37,0:16:05.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s even worse if someone decides for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.71,0:16:07.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,No! No way! Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.16,0:16:09.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can’t afford to make any mistakes right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.67,0:16:13.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have to become the best Simoun sibylla of them all,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.21,0:16:16.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,because as long as I fly a Simoun,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.36,0:16:18.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,I won’t have to go to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.97,0:16:25.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, young ladies,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:27.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,how does it feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.73,0:16:29.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,To be neither a man nor a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:33.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even if I ask, you can’t understand me, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.61,0:16:40.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hormones and surgery made me male right after I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.11,0:16:43.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s how it’s always done in the Archipelago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.45,0:16:46.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,So, I don’t understand…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:49.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Being born with a female body,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.12,0:16:54.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,and being able to decide for yourself whether to become a man or a woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.33,0:16:56.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,what’s it like?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.72,0:17:06.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is he… sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:17:59.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Move, damn it! Fly! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.40,0:18:02.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,What the hell is wrong with you, you demon? Why won’t you fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:11.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry, ladies…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.37,0:18:13.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can’t give this back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.29,0:18:14.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.83,0:18:20.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,If I can just get this home, it will mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.30,0:18:22.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,The skies… will clear…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.55,0:18:27.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have to… no matter what…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:39.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,I told you, you can’t make the Simoun fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.69,0:18:44.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,His Islander friends might come to pick him up, using their aircraft…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.66,0:18:50.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,I won’t hand the Simoun over to them, ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.61,0:19:25.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Help me get him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.54,0:19:26.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,We need to hurry back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:36.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,He’s gotten really stiff…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:38.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let go, let go, let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.09,0:19:42.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Stop it! You’re going to break something!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:50.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Someone will probably come looking for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:51.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,When they get here, they’ll be able to—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.76,0:19:52.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:55.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,We don’t know when the enemy will show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.86,0:19:57.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,We’ve got to get back in the air as soon as we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:20:02.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Besides, there’s no way I can report that I let myself get captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.74,0:20:07.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,If I cut his hands off the controls…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:12.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,There’s nothing else we can do, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.33,0:20:15.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,It can’t be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.46,0:20:18.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone, go wait over there, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.63,0:20:22.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.13,0:21:05.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone! Limone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.88,0:21:07.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Help me move him, Limone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.44,0:21:09.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you still awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:12.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone! Limone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.05,0:21:52.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’ve screwed things up for you again, haven’t I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.51,0:21:56.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,We’ll do the cleanup ourselves, to apologize to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.04,0:21:59.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,You don’t have to do that, Sibylla Aaeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.23,0:22:01.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s okay—we want to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.23,0:22:03.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone, let’s get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:15.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see that they’re cleaning off the Simoun by themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.80,0:22:18.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,It looks like they’re starting to see themselves as priestesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.40,0:22:20.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Maybe…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.88,0:22:29.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry for getting you so dirty.
